                    Text(
                      '${AppStrings.memberSince} ${du.DateUtils.formatMonthYear(seller.memberSince)}',
                      style: AppTextStyles.bodySmall(color: textSecondary),
                    ),
                  ],
                ),
              ],
            ),
          ),

          // ── View listings arrow ────────────────────────────────────────
